.entry-header
Our Story
We want you to feel welcome and relaxed. Our vision here at Hava Kava is to create a place for our human family to come together and have fun. Therefore our Kava Bar & Lounge is for all races, all genders and all cultures.
The History
A Drink Enjoyed For Centuries
Noble Kava root has a rich history of ceremony, social interaction and welcome. Its calming and relaxing benefits are widely known and rigorously studied. From Fiji and Vanuatu, this root has been used as a shared drink by millions of people throughout time. We bring it to you today in delicious flavored teas and exciting potent concoctions. Come on by and connect
Loved by Many
So relaxing and super fun!
L. Kashdan
My favorite place to bring family and friends. Everyone has a blast and I look like the cool guy who knows the secret spot.
G. Stolzberg
Best kava drinks I've ever tasted. Great activities. Comfy couches. Definitely recommend.
S. Ellze
